English

[Verse 1]
Baby I love you, my heart won’t change
Even if our love gets lost for a bit baby
Even if it’s hard, please wait for me my baby
I don’t care if the world turns
Against me, baby baby
I only need you

[Hook]
So baby, promise me That you’ll never leave
Baby, promise me That you’ll love me forever
Baby, promise me Whether I become rich or things get hard
Promise me that we’ll happily grow old together
Baby, promise me, oh please

